{"tid":134225,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"UST 新科目-武術","createTime":"2017-02-25T09:59:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-25T10:17:56.000Z","uid":36995,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f09028866a70ea3a1a531be1db96333a12b17884","tid":134225,"uid":36995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T09:59:37.000Z","msg":"【「叫莊」襲同學案】<br />\n【本報訊】科技大學5間宿生會去年在校園「叫莊」（Chanting）時爆衝突，一名二年級男生涉推撞兩同學，被控兩項襲擊致造成身體傷害罪，案件昨提訊。由於被告將聘私人律師抗辯，案件押後再訊。主任裁判官練錦鴻得悉被告是一名學生後揶揄謂：「讀乜嘢？武術呀？」當值律師索取指示後，指被告讀電子工程系。<br />\n<br />\n案件押後准保釋<br />\n<br />\n被告莊鈞絡（20歲）被控去年2月26日在科大賽馬會大堂襲擊黎俊威及錢卓軒。控方原已準備答辯，但由當值律師代表的被告申請毋須答辯，指被告將聘私人律師代表，亦需索取文件。裁判官押後至下月10日再訊，准他以現金5,000元保釋，不得接觸證人。<br />\n資料顯示當時各學會正進行宣傳期，案發當日是5學生宿生會的「last chant」，逾百人聚集賽馬會大堂叫口號。至晚上情況混亂學生互相推撞。有學生稱遇襲，共5人送院，分別手部受傷及胸口紅腫，科大2014年亦曾發生同類事件。<br />\n案件編號：KTCC369/17<br />\n■記者戴國輝&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20170225/large/a1302a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170225%2Flarge%2Fa1302a.gif&h=60dc70bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20170225/19939809\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20170225%2F19939809&d=Px13HBr2%2FanjjqouUL7W1DANphTrK3OAdhrcB0lChBw%3D&h=2fc753bf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20170225%2F19939809&h=e8db8e61\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20170225/19939809</a>"},{"pid":"679bcf31765795719b304e1b7b92e4d67ed84bf4","tid":134225,"uid":36995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T10:00:29.000Z","msg":"錯台<br />\n自<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"caea069631bb6ef5632f5fa1478885080760b877","tid":134225,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T10:07:47.000Z","msg":"科技武館"},{"pid":"680e0c5b6d9234691fb9a1bc765d6be3d944a6f6","tid":134225,"uid":54486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T10:17:56.000Z","msg":"未入黎都估到係工程毒撚<br />\n<br />\n少接觸女，係女面前即刻英雄上身"}]}